SummaryEnglish: The program consists of the confinement of a variable number of participants in a graphic house, being watched by cameras 24 hours a day, with no connection to the outside world.  Participants cannot communicate with their relatives and friends, read newspapers or other means to obtain external information. These participants are chosen by the production of the program, but they can create whether or not they want to enter the house and have the right to withdraw in the middle of the program.

1.SummaryEnglish:
The BBB18 started on this Monday with a surprise. The eighteenth season will feature four members of a family this first week, and the public will be able to choose two people to stay in the program.
The Lima family consists of Ayrton, 56, his wife Eva, 51, daughter Ana Clara, 20, and their nephew, 22. They were the first to reach the house, and will have a separate space at the beginning. The Lima who remain in the house will be considered a single member. That is, they will only have one vote and, if they go to the wall of elimination, they will go together. The idea is for them to represent your whole family.

2.SummaryEnglish: The second day of Big Brother Brazil was the time to meet 16 participants! The brothers entered the house in groups. The first ones were Paula, Caruso, Gleici and Lucas, followed by Ana Paula, Breno, Nayara and Mahmoud. Then came Kaysar, Jaqueline, Viegas and Mara, and finally, Patrícia, Wagner, Jessica and Diego. And the participants have already taken Immunity Proof!

4.SummaryEnglish: The day of the first test of leadership has come. Who will be the great lucky guy?

85.TitleEnglish: Day 85, 13th Live Eviction, The Last Leader's Competition & 14th Nominations

82.SummaryEnglish: Com a decisão de quem será o novo líder da casa após a prova de resistência, que começou na quinta (4), será formado um paredão duplo. A eliminação acontece no domingo (7).

83.TitleEnglish: Dia 83, 12ª Eliminação, Prova do Líder e Paredão
83.SummaryEnglish: O dia será bastante movimentado, com eliminação de um dos confinados, nova prova do líder e outra formação de paredão.

85.TitleEnglish: Dia 85, 13ª Eliminação, Prova do Líder e Paredão
85.SummaryEnglish: A terça será semelhante ao domingo: um dos participantes será eliminado, acontecerá uma prova do líder e o último paredão será formado.

87.SummaryEnglish: Após a última eliminação, serão conhecidos os três finalistas do Big Brother Brasil 19 e a votação para a final será aberta.

88.SummaryEnglish: Final do BBB19, com a definição do vencedor do prêmio de R$ 1,5 milhão.
